Metadata: University of California Sea Grant College Program
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

A Report on the California Sea Grant College Program for October 1, 1980 to September 30, 1982. This biennial technical report presents the educational, advisory, and research activities undertaken by the California Sea Grant College Program during fiscal years 1980- 81 and \ 981 -82, as required by the National Sea Grant College Program. Unlike Its companion volumes, the 1980-81 and 1981-82 summaries, the biennial report presents the accomplishments of our program in the words of the project leaders who conducted the research. The information is not diluted or summarized — it is meant to be a technical record of our accomplishments for use by individuals in academia, government, and industry.
